        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "こうして1冊の本になったのは、\nお2人の協力のおかげです……！\n図書委員として、こ、心より感謝いたします。",
            "enText": "It is thanks to the cooperation of both \nof you that the book is now available \nat ……! As a member of the library committee, \nI would like to express my heartfelt \nthanks to both of you.",
