        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "私が掲げたテーマは“流行”。\nイマドキの学生が読みたくなる本の紹介だ。",
            "enText": "My theme was \"Trends. I wanted to introduce a \nbook that the current generation of students \nwould want to read.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 10,
                    "pathId": 3253114440052097583
                },
                {
