        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "なにせ学会で発表されたばかりの、\n最先端レース理論が掲載されている\n書籍ばかりだからな！",
            "enText": "They are all books that contain cutting-edge \nrace theory that has just been presented at \nan academic conference!",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 102,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 113,
                    "pathId": -6372827391141540580
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 130,
