            "pathId": 4969395540058221209,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "おお。紹介されている本を読めば、\n“流行”になりそうな理論をいち早く\nチェックできるわけですね！",
            "enText": "Oh. If I read the books you mentioned, I can \ncheck out the theories that are about to \nbecome I can check out the theories that are \nabout to become \"trendy\"!",
