        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "“流行”に敏感なイマドキの方たちにも\n興味を持っていただけると思います……！",
            "enText": "We think it will be of interest \nto the \"trendy\" and fashion-conscious \npeople of today. ……!",
