            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "“夢”への道標となるマネジメント術。\nそれを身につけられる数々の本を、\nコラム形式で紹介してみました。",
            "enText": "Management skills that will guide you to your \n\"dream\". I have introduced a number of books \nthat will help you acquire these skills in \nthe form of columns. I introduce them in the \nform of columns.",
