        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "なるほど！　ラインナップは\nビジネス本中心だが、学生向けに\n読み解き方を解説しているのか。",
            "enText": "I see! The lineup is mainly business books, \nbut you're explaining how to read and \nunderstand them for students?",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 115,
                    "pathId": 4792687256716593854
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
