            "pathId": -7479583300201764204,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ビワハヤヒデ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ほう……発表当時の17世紀の歴史的背景を\n紐解きつつ、現代的な解釈を補足して\nユニークさを際立たせるという狙いだな。",
            "enText": "The aim is to highlight the uniqueness of the \nwork by tying it to the historical background \nof the 17th century at the time of its \npublication, while supplementing it with \nmodern interpretations. I guess the aim is to \nhighlight the uniqueness of the work.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 120,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 132,
                    "pathId": 6756375960359733910
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 131,
                    "pathId": -8619691863721572115
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 131,
                    "pathId": 8241006053361778244
                }
