            "pathId": 2597459573594519264,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ここで紹介された本を読んだ上で、\nドン・キホーテに触れれば\n爆笑は間違いなしでしょう……！",
            "enText": "If you read the books mentioned here \nand then mention Don Quixote, you're \nsure to have a blast. ……!",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": -3724485822683160554
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
