            "pathId": -8426033223608840600,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "は、はい……！　このフリー誌を\nきっかけに読書の輪が広まると思うと……\nすごく楽しみです……！",
            "enText": "Ha, yes ……! I'm so excited that this \nfree magazine will be the start of \na wider reading circle.…… I'm really \nlooking forward to it: ……!",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 106,
            "animData": [
